WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.835
The financial transactions are fully handled by Amazon. The customer

00:00:03.835 --> 00:00:07.670
pays for our platform through their existing billing framework. Amazon

00:00:07.670 --> 00:00:11.506
manages the backend complexity and disburses the payment directly to

00:00:11.506 --> 00:00:15.341
AppsFlyer. This step-by-step process ensures there is no confusion about

00:00:15.341 --> 00:00:19.176
how AppsFlyer gets paid.
